<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">
  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFrameworks>net8.0;net10.0</TargetFrameworks>
    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>
    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>
    <PackageId>FluxFlow.Components.Routing</PackageId>
    <AssemblyName>FluxFlow.Components.Routing</AssemblyName>
    <RootNamespace>FluxFlow.Components.Routing</RootNamespace>
    <Version>3.0.0</Version>
    <Authors>FluxFlow contributors</Authors>
    <Description>Standalone routing nodes for FluxFlow: switch, fork, merge, window, correlation, and join over the FluxFlow.Nodes kit, with broadcast output/error/event ports. Predicate/key extraction comes from FluxFlow.Mapping. No engine required.</Description>
    <PackageTags>workflow;dataflow;components;routing</PackageTags>
    <PackageLicenseExpression>MIT</PackageLicenseExpression>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>Rebuilt on the FluxFlow.Nodes kit: flow.switch/fork/window/correlation are FlowNode&lt;TInput, ...&gt; transforms and flow.merge is a fan-in FlowNode&lt;TInput, TInput&gt;, all carrying the message correlation id and timing off an injected TimeProvider; flow.join is built directly on kit primitives with two typed inputs (Left/Right), a result Output, and a Timeouts output. Each node takes its options record, key/predicate selectors (IFlowPredicate / IFlowExpressionEngine from FluxFlow.Mapping), and a TimeProvider directly. The engine factories, module, registration extensions, design-metadata provider, the definition-options reader, and the string-to-Type / expression-registry resolution layer are removed; the package depends only on FluxFlow.Nodes and FluxFlow.Mapping (runs without the engine).</PackageReleaseNotes>
    <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
    <PackageReadmeFile>README.md</PackageReadmeFile>
    <IncludeSymbols>true</IncludeSymbols>
    <SymbolPackageFormat>snupkg</SymbolPackageFormat>
  </PropertyGroup>
  <ItemGroup>
    <ProjectReference Include="..\FluxFlow.Nodes\FluxFlow.Nodes.csproj" />
    <ProjectReference Include="..\FluxFlow.Mapping\FluxFlow.Mapping.csproj" />
  </ItemGroup>
  <ItemGroup>
    <PackageReference Include="System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow" Version="9.0.4" NoWarn="NU1510" />
  </ItemGroup>
  <ItemGroup>
    <None Include="README.md" Pack="true" PackagePath="\" />
  </ItemGroup>
</Project>
